description: The guests may have all left but for host Carter Woods, the party isn't over just yet, at least not if Quin Quire has any say in the matter. He's the last to leave, helping Carter with the mess clean up, but if he has his way, this is one party that's ready to move to the bedroom. Carter is definitely in the mood and takes Quin up on his offer, and then proceeds to show Quin exactly why he's such a good host, giving Quin all the party flavor he could ask for, and then some.Enjoy!
title: Party Flavor
